				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The DMA process always starts at $xx00 and ends at $xxFF.
<br />
<br />The point is that on some frames you start from $0200 and write through $02FF, and on other frames you start from $0280 and write through $02FF, then wrap back to $0200 and write through $027F.</div>

